{
  "stem": "4113.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So the Jews scrambled together whatever they had-- if they had diamond rings, gold, and [? sold-- ?] sold on the black market to deliver these monies to the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "When I think about it nowadays, I personally think that they didn't have the transportation.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You see, they had it arranged for that day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But apparently, the transportation didn't come along.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So they said, now, if you'll pay us so much money, we will, you know, rescind the order.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So they rescinded it for a few days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Then again two times they rescinded it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Finally, we all had to show up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Now, the evening before, we wanted to know what's going to be.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So I and my half cousin took a few plates of glass as if going to work and went to the Gestapo headquarters.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They now had their living place was in a villa a little bit away from where we were.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We walked over there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "The maid that used to be-- used to work for them-- used to cook for them-- we knew very well because she was a  maid to a Jewish neighbor of ours.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So her name was [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hela. ?] So my cousin and myself went there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Hela ?] opens the door.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we told [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Hela ?] that we wanted to talk to Schmatsler, the head of the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so she went in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember I peeked in through the door.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was a whole bunch them sitting eating and drinking, you know, including Gestapo not from our town.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They sat at the very long table.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Schmatsler come in-- comes out with his food still in this mouth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he immediately sensed what we were there for.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, glasermeister, you are going to stay like this.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
